list_page_teaser: Sarah & Jacob have been going together for many years.  Click and maybe you can learn how they make their relationship last!
description_html:
Sarah and Jacob are parents now, and have been together for many years.

Hopefully they will share some of their tips for how they make their relationship last. Check back soon for updates!
story_html:
I met Sarah and Jacob at the Goth clubs in Denver and Fort Collins here in Colorado.

They have relocated to the Pacific Northwest and we have been out of touch. I wanted to have something for them to look at before asking them to share their story.

I apologize for not yet having the tips hinted at in the teaser on the gallery page. Please be patient — this sort of work takes a long time! I do all this work myself, and I am not yet making any money off it!

To learn when I update the site, follow us on social media or join the email list!
